msgstr "第2步：描述已实施的与目标相关的行动"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:96
msgid ""
"Areas of implemented action (projects and initiatives on the ground) related"
" to the targets can be reported on in table SO1.IA.T1."
msgstr "表 SO1.IA.T1 报告了与目标相关的已实施行动领域（实地项目和举措）。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:98
msgid ""
"If Parties already reported implemented actions in PRAIS as part of their "
"2022 national report, they will be pre-filled in this table."
msgstr "如果缔约方在其 2022 年国家报告中已在 PRAIS 中报告了已实施的行动，则这些行动将预先填入本表。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:100
msgid ""
"As in SO1-VT.T1, Parties have the same three options to manage the existing "
"implemented actions in the reporting form (i.e. edit, remove or add new "
"implemented actions)."
msgstr "与 SO1-VT.T1 中一样，缔约方在报告表中有三个相同的选项来管理现有的已执行行动（即编辑、删除或添加新的已执行行动）。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:102
msgid ""
"Ideally the implemented actions should correspond to specific targets "
"declared in SO1-VT.T1. However Parties can report new implemented actions "
"that are not specifically addressing an existing SO1 voluntary target."
msgstr ""
"理想情况下，已实施的行动应与 SO1-VT.T1 中宣布的具体目标相对应。不过，缔约方也可以报告新的已实施行动，但这些行动不应专门针对现有的 SO1 "
"自愿性目标。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:104
msgid ""
"When reporting a new action or editing an existing one, the actions should "
"be described, their location presented, as well as the start date for the "
"action and the areal extent (in km2). In addition, the source of funding to "
"implement the action should be described using one of the options presented "
"in the dropdown menu. As this is a new field, Parties should update actions "
"previously reported with the source of funding (if applicable). As for Step "
"1, subnational areas of implemented action should ideally be delineated in "
"the PRAIS 4 spatial data viewer."
msgstr ""
"在报告新行动或编辑现有行动时，应说明行动、行动地点、行动开始日期和行动范围（平方公 "
"里）。此外，应使用下拉菜单中的任一选项说明实施行动的资金来源。由于这是一个新字段，缔约方应更新以前报告的行动，并注明资金来源（如适用）。与步骤 1 "
"一样，最好在 PRAIS 4 空间数据查看器中划定已实施行动的国家以下各级区域。"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:106
msgid ""
"Delineating voluntary targets and related actions currently under "
"implementation can help track progress towards achieving LDN in a country by"
" 2030, support the quantification of any remaining gaps and develop "
"scenarios for closing those gaps. In addition, the UNCCD can use this "
"spatial data to create information products to demonstrate the impact of the"
" Convention and global progress towards LDN."
msgstr ""
"划定了自愿目标和目前正在实施的相关行动后，将有助于跟踪一国到2030年实现LDN的进展情况，支持量化任何剩余的差距，并制定缩小这些差距的方案。此外，《荒漠化公约》可以利用这一空间数据创建信息产品，以展示《公约》的影响和全球在实现LDN方面的进展。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:108
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:168
msgid "Step 3. Save form and make available for review"
msgstr "步骤 3.保存表格并提供审查"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:110
msgid ""
"Parties have the option to include additional information in the ‘General "
"Comments’ field to add any relevant information or to report on specific "
"country or regional situations."
msgstr "缔约方可以选择在 \"一般性评论 \"栏中添加任何相关信息，或报告具体国家或地区的情况。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:112
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:170
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:194
msgid ""
"Once the form has been completed and verified by the Parties, it should be "
"marked as “In Review” and saved. Once the UNCCD has completed its review and"
" any review comments have been resolved by the Parties, the form can be "
"marked as “Finalized” and saved."
msgstr ""
"表格完成并经缔约方核实后，应标记为 \"审查中 \"并保存。一旦《防治荒漠化公约》完成审查，且缔约方解决了任何审查意见，即可将表格标记为 \"已定稿 "
"\"并保存。"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:114
msgid "6.1.4. Dependencies"
msgstr "6.1.4. 依赖性"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:116
msgid ""
"Although there is no direct dependency between the voluntary targets and SO "
"1 indicators, it is expected that the results of the geospatial analyses for"
" the estimation of the proportion of degraded land will inform the "
"definition and spatial delineation of the voluntary targets and related "
"projects and initiatives on the ground."
msgstr ""
"尽管自愿目标和SO "
"1的指标之间没有直接的依赖关系，但预计用于估计已退化土地比例的地理空间分析结果将为自愿目标的定义和空间划分以及实地的相关项目和倡议提供信息。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:118
msgid ""
"There is a dependency between the targets set in table SO1-VT.T1 and the "
"implemented actions reported in SO1.IA.T1; each reported action in table "
"SO1.IA.T1 should correspond to one or more targets reported in SO1-VT.T1. "
"However, Parties can still report actions with no link to an existing "
"voluntary target."
msgstr ""
"表SO1-VT.T1中设定的目标与SO1.IA.T1中报告的已执行行动之间存在依赖关系；表SO1.IA.T1中报告的每项行动都应与SO1-VT.T1中报告的一项或多项目标相对应。然而，缔约方仍可报告与现有自愿目标无关联的行动。"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:120
msgid "6.1.5. Challenges"
msgstr "6.1.5. 挑战"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:122
msgid "National coordination"
msgstr "国家协调"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:124
msgid ""
"With respect to the various plans and commitments formulated under the Rio "
"Conventions and/or other related initiatives, there is the risk of lack of "
"coherence, overlap and duplication of efforts. There is scope for better "
"alignment on restoration in national plans between the three Rio "
"Conventions, which could enhance planning and implementation."
msgstr ""
"根据《里约公约》和/或其他相关倡议制定的各种计划和承诺存在着缺乏一致性、工作重叠和重复的风险。里约三公约之间的国家计划在恢复方面有待进一步协调，从而加强国家计划的规划和执行。"

#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:126
msgid ""
"National voluntary targets need to be well-defined, measurable and time-"
"bound to monitor progress. The availability of GIS tools in PRAIS 4 may "
"support the definition of more accurate and realistic targets in defined "
"locations."
msgstr "国家自愿目标需要明确界定、可衡量和有时限，以监测进展情况。PRAIS 4中的地理信息系统工具可以支持在确定的地点定义更准确和更现实的目标。"

